org.cyclops.cyclopscore.persist.nbt

Annotation Type NBTPersist


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface NBTPersist
    If this field should be persisted in Tile Entities. Fields that are a subtype of INBTSerializable must not be null, they should have a dummy value that will then be populated with the actual values. It will automatically be added to CyclopsTileEntity.writeToNBT(net.minecraft.nbt.NBTTagCompound) and CyclopsTileEntity.readFromNBT(net.minecraft.nbt.NBTTagCompound).

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      boolean useDefaultValue
      If set to true, NBT tags that don't contain the key for this field will return a default value as set by Cyclops.

    • Element Detail

      • useDefaultValue

        public abstract boolean useDefaultValue
        If set to true, NBT tags that don't contain the key for this field will return a default value as set by Cyclops. Otherwise, NBT tags that don't contain a key for this field will not be overwritten.
        Returns:
        true if non-existing NBT keys are overwritten with a default value, or false otherwise.
        Default:
        true
